title: Big Sean's "I Decided." Will Debut At #1: Report
text:
Home > Music > Big Sean's "I Decided." Will Debut At #1: Report Big Sean's "I Decided." Will Debut At #1: Report 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 7, 2017 at 05:25pm Big Sean will likely take the top spot on the Billboard 200. 
Big Sean 's I Decided. will likely debut at number one, Billboard reports . The album is projected to sell 120,000 equivalent album units. Last week, Migos ' Culture debuted at number one with 131,000 album sales. 
I Decided. will be Sean's fourth consecutive album to debut in the top five. His 2015 album Dark Sky Paradise earned 173,000 sales in its first week.
